title: #10 - Top of the Month (Talking About Jake Paul, Lance Stewart, Jerry Seinfeld)
description: Today we open up a new format called "Top of the Month", where we discuss all the best stories and videos that propped up during the month. Today we talk about Jake Paul Live Show, Lance stewart's new videos and Jerry Seinfeld being a dick (or not).
